<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 22:07:10 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>白宫证实哈马斯高级军事指挥官马尔万·伊萨上周在以色列对加沙的袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/white-house-hamas-deputy-military-chief-marwan-issa-was-killed-in-israeli-gaza-strike/0000018e-535e-d37a-a1ae-5b7ed5ca0000</link><description>尚未收到以色列关于伊萨死亡的官方确认。他是穆罕默德·代伊夫的得力助手，并担任哈马斯武装部队副总司令</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 21:57:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/white-house-hamas-deputy-military-chief-marwan-issa-was-killed-in-israeli-gaza-strike/0000018e-535e-d37a-a1ae-5b7ed5ca0000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普：任何投票给民主党的犹太人都讨厌他们的宗教，应该为自己感到羞耻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/trump-jews-who-vote-for-democrats-hate-everything-about-israel-should-be-ashamed/0000018e-5371-dca4-ad8e-f7ff5c090000</link><description>这位前总统还指责查克·舒默“反以色列”以赢得选票</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 21:31:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/trump-jews-who-vote-for-democrats-hate-everything-about-israel-should-be-ashamed/0000018e-5371-dca4-ad8e-f7ff5c090000</guid></item><item><title>拜登与内塔尼亚胡通话后，美国拒绝拉法“稻草人”论点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/u-s-rejects-rafah-straw-man-argument-after-biden-netanyahu-call/0000018e-5300-dca4-ad8e-f7fee8f60000</link><description>拜登总统结束一个多月以来与内塔尼亚胡的首次通话后不久，美国国家安全顾问杰克·沙利文表示，以色列总理反对在拉法采取重大军事行动类似于反对彻底击败哈马斯的立场是“无稽之谈”</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 19:55:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/u-s-rejects-rafah-straw-man-argument-after-biden-netanyahu-call/0000018e-5300-dca4-ad8e-f7fee8f60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙城 Al-Shifa 医院袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-combat-during-al-shifa-hospital-raid-in-gaza-city/0000018e-52df-d282-a19f-7fdfcfc50000</link><description>根据陆军记录，20 岁的参谋军士。来自耶路撒冷的马坦·维诺格拉多夫是自 10 月地面行动开始以来第 250 名阵亡士兵</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 19:49:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldier-killed-in-combat-during-al-shifa-hospital-raid-in-gaza-city/0000018e-52df-d282-a19f-7fdfcfc50000</guid></item><item><title>欧盟“一致”同意对暴力的以色列约旦河西岸定居者实施制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/eu-unanimously-agrees-to-impose-sanctions-against-violent-israeli-west-bank-settlers/0000018e-52c2-dc23-a3bf-daf760d20000</link><description>这一举措是继美国和英国之后，得到欧盟所有27个成员国同意的。它涉及对约旦河西岸“暴力”以色列定居者的旅行禁令和资产冻结，并禁止欧盟公民与目标开展业务</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 18:59:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/eu-unanimously-agrees-to-impose-sanctions-against-violent-israeli-west-bank-settlers/0000018e-52c2-dc23-a3bf-daf760d20000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日的隐形受害者：即使死亡，以色列的寻求庇护者也得不到承认</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-invisible-victims-of-oct-7-even-in-death-asylum-seekers-in-israel-arent-recognized/0000018e-5277-db53-a39e-daf704f30000</link><description>吉吉、泰格和彪马逃离厄立特里亚和达尔富尔，获准在以色列生活，但没有合法身份或权利。 10月7日他们被哈马斯杀害后，国家拒绝将他们视为恐怖主义受害者</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 18:19:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-invisible-victims-of-oct-7-even-in-death-asylum-seekers-in-israel-arent-recognized/0000018e-5277-db53-a39e-daf704f30000</guid></item><item><title>您需要了解的第 164 天：以色列拒绝近东救济工程处主要人员进入加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-164-israel-denies-unrwa-chief-entry-to-gaza/0000018e-52aa-dca4-ad8e-f6fe40a10001</link><description>摩萨德负责人抵达卡塔尔，就释放人质/停火协议进行新一轮谈判 ■ 以色列国防军称，“具体证据”显示哈马斯正在使用希法医院，因此在袭击中逮捕了 80 多人 ■ 以色列拒绝近东救济工程处负责人入境前往加沙 ■ 内塔尼亚胡总理一个多月以来首次与拜登通电话，但没有像往常一样发布谈话内容 ■ 战争结束 164 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 17:51:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-164-israel-denies-unrwa-chief-entry-to-gaza/0000018e-52aa-dca4-ad8e-f6fe40a10001</guid></item><item><title>以色列队抵达卡塔尔；以色列高级官员称，哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔将参与会谈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-team-touches-down-in-qatar-for-next-round-of-gaza-talks-with-hamas/0000018e-524e-dfaa-af8e-d3cf36aa0000</link><description>一位以色列高级政治消息人士称，谈判将“直接与哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔”进行，而不是与调解人进行，预计将需要“至少两周”</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 17:41:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-team-touches-down-in-qatar-for-next-round-of-gaza-talks-with-hamas/0000018e-524e-dfaa-af8e-d3cf36aa0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登和比比打架，特朗普和共和党闻到了血腥味</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-18/ty-article/.highlight/biden-and-bibi-are-fighting-and-trump-and-the-gop-smell-blood/0000018e-51f5-dfaa-af8e-d3ffd7db0001</link><description>随着民主党和内塔尼亚胡之间的紧张关系呈指数级增长，与加沙的死亡人数同步，以色列总理希望急于利用这场危机打击拜登的特朗普和共和党能为他提供政治救生筏</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 17:31:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-18/ty-article/.highlight/biden-and-bibi-are-fighting-and-trump-and-the-gop-smell-blood/0000018e-51f5-dfaa-af8e-d3ffd7db0001</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列试管受精实验室负责人因涉嫌故意进口携带遗传病的卵子而被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-ivf-lab-heads-arrested-for-allegedly-knowingly-importing-eggs-with-disease/0000018e-51d7-dca4-ad8e-f5ff250c0000</link><description>调查是在一名患者死产、另一名患者生下一名患有血友病的婴儿后开始的。以色列卫生部现在命令体外受精部门寻找从同一诊所接受卵子的妇女，以便告知她们风险</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 17:26:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-ivf-lab-heads-arrested-for-allegedly-knowingly-importing-eggs-with-disease/0000018e-51d7-dca4-ad8e-f5ff250c0000</guid></item><item><title>联合国支持的报告称，加沙很快将面临饥荒；欧盟高级外交官指责以色列“挑起”饥饿</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/un-report-gaza-will-soon-face-famine-eu-top-diplomat-blames-israel-of-provoking-hunger/0000018e-5229-dfaa-af8e-d3eb3d060000</link><description>报告称，加沙约有一半人口目前面临“灾难性饥饿”。联合国敦促人道主义援助完全进入加沙，官员们称这是一场“人为”灾难。与此同时，以色列表示问题在于援助的分配</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 16:22:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/un-report-gaza-will-soon-face-famine-eu-top-diplomat-blames-israel-of-provoking-hunger/0000018e-5229-dfaa-af8e-d3eb3d060000</guid></item><item><title>对于以色列人和巴勒斯坦人来说，是否有一条“从地狱到共存的道路”？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/for-israelis-and-palestinians-is-there-a-pathway-from-hell-to-coexistence/0000018e-4d2a-d011-afef-7f7ecc730000</link><description>10月7日之后巴以关系如何？它们到底存在吗？两国解决方案已死吗？宗教原教旨主义在加沙战争中扮演什么角色？国土报-加州大学洛杉矶分校联合会议上的四位小组成员质疑我们是如何走到这一步的，以及如何以及是否有前进的道路</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 15:54:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/for-israelis-and-palestinians-is-there-a-pathway-from-hell-to-coexistence/0000018e-4d2a-d011-afef-7f7ecc730000</guid></item><item><title>格兰特在内阁会议上抨击斯莫特里奇，称他不会允许将以色列军队变成“民兵”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/gallant-blasts-far-right-smotrich-says-he-wont-allow-turning-israel-army-to-a-militia/0000018e-51a8-dad4-a9ff-5ff9dd070000</link><description>在斯莫特里奇告诉以色列国防军参谋长他反对额外任命陆军高级官员后，国防部长指责财政部长破坏国防机构</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 15:32:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/gallant-blasts-far-right-smotrich-says-he-wont-allow-turning-israel-army-to-a-militia/0000018e-51a8-dad4-a9ff-5ff9dd070000</guid></item><item><title>如何一步步摧毁以色列的新闻自由</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-communications-minister-is-destroying-the-free-press/0000018e-5195-dad4-a9ff-5fddba2a0000</link><description>给朋友好处，给对手惩罚：以色列通讯部长什洛莫·卡希正在利用加沙战争推进一系列旨在破坏该国媒体的措施</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 15:24:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-communications-minister-is-destroying-the-free-press/0000018e-5195-dad4-a9ff-5fddba2a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡告诉 AIPAC：“极端边缘团体”决定了他的政策，这是一个“故意的谎言”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tells-aipac-brass-its-a-deliberate-lie-that-hes-beholden-to-extremists/0000018e-51f4-d1dc-a3ce-fffde4320000</link><description>总理向 AIPAC 来访委员会坚称，以色列公众不支持他在加沙政策的想法是“谎言”。他还反驳了拜登政府和国际社会坚持以色列不应入侵拉法的立场，称“我们的部队可以去任何地方”</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 14:54:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-tells-aipac-brass-its-a-deliberate-lie-that-hes-beholden-to-extremists/0000018e-51f4-d1dc-a3ce-fffde4320000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日之后，世界中央厨房为以色列人提供食物。现在它正在为加沙的饥饿者提供食物</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/world-central-kitchen-fed-israelis-after-oct-7-now-its-feeding-the-starving-in-gaza/0000018e-4d1a-d282-a19f-7ddb719d0000</link><description>世界中央厨房是由魅力十足的名厨何塞·安德烈斯领导的慈善机构，本周末组织了第一艘船向绝望的巴勒斯坦人运送粮食援助。那么安德烈斯和他的团队如何在加沙战争双方之间游刃有余呢？</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 14:50:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article-magazine/.premium/world-central-kitchen-fed-israelis-after-oct-7-now-its-feeding-the-starving-in-gaza/0000018e-4d1a-d282-a19f-7ddb719d0000</guid></item><item><title>儿子于10月7日被杀的前部长呼吁以色列释放“卑鄙的凶手”以解救人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/former-minister-calls-for-israel-to-release-despicable-murders-to-return-hostages/0000018e-5186-d282-a19f-7dd7a2b10000</link><description>前部长伊扎尔·谢伊（Izhar Shay）的儿子亚龙于 10 月 7 日在行动中丧生，他在推特上表示，如果这意味着从加沙地带夺回剩余的以色列人质，他希望以色列释放杀害他儿子的凶手和其他“卑鄙的努赫巴恐怖分子”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 13:22:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/former-minister-calls-for-israel-to-release-despicable-murders-to-return-hostages/0000018e-5186-d282-a19f-7dd7a2b10000</guid></item><item><title>从无人机到建筑：美国的制裁可能会损害对西岸非法前哨基地的捐款</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/american-sanctions-liable-to-hurt-donations-to-illegal-west-bank-outposts/0000018e-50f8-d282-a19f-7df9b0fe0000</link><description>美国决定制裁前哨基地而不仅仅是个别定居者，这意味着华盛顿对待以色列西岸政策的态度进一步升级。目前正在为受制裁前哨基地建设进行的筹款活动可能会受到影响</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 12:47:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/american-sanctions-liable-to-hurt-donations-to-illegal-west-bank-outposts/0000018e-50f8-d282-a19f-7df9b0fe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列学术界会公开反对军队在加沙的行动吗？决不</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/will-israeli-academia-speak-out-against-the-armys-actions-in-gaza-no-way/0000018e-4d97-dc34-a18e-ff9f21fc0000</link><description>除了作为一名记者我从不签署请愿书之外，我对以色列学术机构没有积极的期望，所以我没有签署针对希伯来大学教授停职的抗议信</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 12:07:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-18/ty-article-opinion/.premium/will-israeli-academia-speak-out-against-the-armys-actions-in-gaza-no-way/0000018e-4d97-dc34-a18e-ff9f21fc0000</guid></item><item><title>希伯来大学停职教授院长反对她返回，如果她不放弃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/dean-of-lecturer-suspended-from-israeli-university-opposes-her-reinstatement/0000018e-512c-dca4-ad8e-f5fe243e0000</link><description>社会工作学院院长于10月7日宣布，要求Shalhoub-Kevorkian教授必须对否认强奸和谋杀表示遗憾</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 12:00:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-18/ty-article/.premium/dean-of-lecturer-suspended-from-israeli-university-opposes-her-reinstatement/0000018e-512c-dca4-ad8e-f5fe243e0000</guid></item></channel></rss>